---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="OpenVila Astro Demo">
  <section>
    <h2>Website Overview</h2>
    <p>
      This Astro demo is designed for OpenVila scanning tests. It includes user-facing pages such as
      pricing, FAQ, user agreement, and privacy policy.
    </p>
    <p>
      Suggested flow: run <code>openvila init</code>, then <code>openvila scan</code>, and inspect
      <code>.openvila/knowledges/index.md</code>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
